ion-al-mustahab","tag-virtue-al-fadail","tag-voluntary-prayers-salat-nafilah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9qj","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":31737,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/private-voluntary-salat-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":36227,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Voluntary prayer better in private","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Suhayb ibn Sinan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer in congregation is like performing twenty-give prayers alone. Voluntary prayer where no one can see him is like performing twenty-five prayers under the eyes of people.\u201d Source: al-Targhi\u0304b fi\u0304 Fad\u0323a\u0304'il al-A'ma\u0304l li-Ibn Sha\u0304hi\u0304n 67\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36229,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/21\/nafl-salat-better-home\/","url_meta":{"origin":36227,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary prayers greater at home","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Damrah ibn Habib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe voluntary prayer of a man in his house is greater than his voluntary prayer in front of people, just as the congregational prayer is better than the prayer of a man alone.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36412,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/salat-al-duha-tawbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36227,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Salat al-Duha is prayer of repentant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone preserve the forenoon prayer but the penitent. It is the prayer of the penitent.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 1224 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32614,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/03\/nawafil-salat-separated\/","url_meta":{"origin":36227,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary prayers separated from obligatory prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyyah reported: When you perform the Friday prayer, do not pray another prayer until you have spoken or left the mosque. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, commanded us to do that, to not connect two prayers together unless we have spoken or we have left.\u2026","rel":"","context":"I